From: Aleksandrs Vinarskis <alex.vinarskis@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 25 May 2025 13:48:35 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 07/12] arm64: dts: qcom: x1e78100-lenovo-thinkpad-t14s: Enable
 4 lane DP mode

With 4 lane DP support added to QMP PHY, allow 4 lanes on both Type-C
connectors.

Signed-off-by: Aleksandrs Vinarskis <alex.vinarskis@gmail.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/x1e78100-lenovo-thinkpad-t14s.dtsi | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/x1e78100-lenovo-thinkpad-t14s.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/x1e78100-lenovo-thinkpad-t14s.dtsi
index ac1dddf27da3..e79b5067bbac 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/x1e78100-lenovo-thinkpad-t14s.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/x1e78100-lenovo-thinkpad-t14s.dtsi
@@ -994,7 +994,7 @@ &mdss_dp0 {
 };
 
 &mdss_dp0_out {
-	data-lanes = <0 1>;
+	data-lanes = <0 1 2 3>;
 };
 
 &mdss_dp1 {
@@ -1002,7 +1002,7 @@ &mdss_dp1 {
 };
 
 &mdss_dp1_out {
-	data-lanes = <0 1>;
+	data-lanes = <0 1 2 3>;
 };
 
 &mdss_dp3 {
